    <string name="setup_instructions">How to use this keyboard:\n\n1. Make sure the Backend Server URL above is correct (Render cloud URL).\n2. Tap Test Connection — it should say the server is online.\n3. Tap Save Settings.\n4. Open Android Settings → System → Languages &amp; input → On-screen keyboard.\n5. Enable \"Keyword Record Keyboard\".\n6. Select it as your default keyboard.\n\nEvery key you type is saved to MongoDB with a unique record ID.\nView records at your server URL in a browser.</string>
